{"tid":273150,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發！] 愛禮信中學生參觀東方報業中心！","createTime":"2017-06-06T10:45:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-17T07:39:38.000Z","uid":319,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d149f1094cb19a1b03a2f8f0d829d2c06454ffa2","tid":273150,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T10:45:13.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】新媒體發展一日千里，除了傳統印刷報紙外，東方報業集團正全力發展網上新聞平台《東網》，讓讀者瀏覽最快、最新、最準確及最詳盡的新聞資訊。廿九名迦密愛禮信中學的學生昨日參觀東方報業中心，了解印刷及網上新聞嚴謹的製作過程。<br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170414/photo/0414-00176-093b1.jpg?t=1496745862232\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170414%2Fphoto%2F0414-00176-093b1.jpg%3Ft%3D1496745862232&h=72fb827b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n迦密愛禮信中學的學生昨日參觀東方報業中心。（梁耀榮攝）<br />\n<br />\n廿九名學生昨日參觀東方報業中心多個部門，包括突發部、美術部和印刷廠房等。他們走入ontv東網電視節目製作室時特別雀躍，不少同學更嘗試當娛樂主播，一邊看字幕一邊讀稿。<br />\n<br />\n就讀中五的張雨璇表示，參觀突發部即時新聞令她眼界大開，更令她明白新聞工作需要分工處理。同樣就讀中五的陳錦雯則對資料部最感興趣，她指《東方日報》歷史悠久，資料內容非常豐富，她從中發現新聞行業正不斷進步。<br />\n<br />\n迦密愛禮信中學中文科老師黃家鏘表示，現時不少學生使用新聞Apps閱讀新聞，校方希望透過安排參觀報業活動，擴闊學生視野，讓他們了解報業運作流程，並學習處事爭分奪秒、事事求真的態度。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170414/00176_093.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170414%2F00176_093.html&d=nsKiQur%2FxJnSfmrrLqXCD26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=2bf6a416\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170414/00176_093.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa5aa1b8f728ea784ddcb9810346c40db0690090","tid":273150,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T10:46:19.000Z","msg":"上次我間母校去參觀都上報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06615844dd95110fad151c052a86d2128ea37faf","tid":273150,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T10:48:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上次我間母校去參觀都上報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"915e73aee4ef911fc0d2566bdd31b5904f2ed488","tid":273150,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T10:50:25.000Z","msg":"唔使考試咩"},{"pid":"9f05f943bb8ec41712ed4795f8a1ec911601bb58","tid":273150,"uid":319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T11:10:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔使考試咩</blockquote><br />\n4月的"},{"pid":"12d7633504c806be40acd220d939fa983de253fd","tid":273150,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T11:16:25.000Z","msg":"有冇介紹創辦人歷史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0b0a9b0fc2c3d951abe54fd2a6a8c1884100598","tid":273150,"uid":35468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T13:12:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.twword.com/uploads/wiki/0b/21/47181_0.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.twword.com%2Fuploads%2Fwiki%2F0b%2F21%2F47181_0.gif&h=1ae86aec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c925ea091a8b64c61f99ba13d0745fec984064bd","tid":273150,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T13:15:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"02229fc13300031015c01f2f8673c2135b59ce1d","tid":273150,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T13:17:21.000Z","msg":"在2012年3月8日，《東方日報》報導指東方報業集團成功「起底」，找出高登討論區會員「徐晃」、「去支」及「一時俊傑」的真實姓名，並成功透過法律途徑向該三名網民作出追討"},{"pid":"956abf4a2feca693f938542e96f542c7073349ea","tid":273150,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T13:18:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7b4dc9b1daa8f65357018d1dc0b2f66990f610b8","t